Best,
Amanda", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "Re: CRM Software Budget Inquiry", "from": "michael.jensen@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Michael Jensen", "to": ["amanda.lee@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2025-01-05 10:45:00", "body": "Hi Amanda,

