Best,
Michael", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "Re: CRM Software Budget Inquiry", "from": "amanda.lee@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Amanda Lee", "to": ["michael.jensen@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["john.davis@elexionautomotive.com", "lisa.brown@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2025-01-05 11:15:00", "body": "Michael,

Thank you for your swift response. The $108,000 investment in our CRM system has provided us with invaluable customer behavior data that we will be leveraging to drive sales in 2025.

